  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/68b9b68a36cca4c8a984853658ddf7d4.webp?t=1746142050\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/3d6c726168396d9afae74f6cc45fea4d.poster.avif?t=1746142050\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/3d6c726168396d9afae74f6cc45fea4d.webm?t=1746142050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/3d6c726168396d9afae74f6cc45fea4d.mp4?t=1746142050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Salvage Protocol</strong> is a single-player horror game about infiltrating abandoned space stations. Break anything in sight, recover valuable components, dodge traps and fight off terrifying monsters hiding in plain sight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And maybe one day YOU will pay off your debt to the S.R.P.O. mega-corp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/a08430efd872ffcb22a54584c76f2b13.poster.avif?t=1746142050\" width=800 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/a08430efd872ffcb22a54584c76f2b13.webm?t=1746142050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/a08430efd872ffcb22a54584c76f2b13.mp4?t=1746142050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/fa497bea5e043753f11f979781005c91.webp?t=1746142050\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak through vents, climb unstable structures and reactivate ancient machines to open new paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every station is a handcrafted maze where death is lurking just around the corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/41318fd258a9221f2cf2ec36cceb537c.poster.avif?t=1746142050\" width=798 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/41318fd258a9221f2cf2ec36cceb537c.webm?t=1746142050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/41318fd258a9221f2cf2ec36cceb537c.mp4?t=1746142050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/c4194979712f104793120f00085bdb9a.webp?t=1746142050\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If it looks like you can break it, you probably can.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wreak havoc and collect scrap to satisfy S.R.P.O’s endless appetite for worthless junk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/ee3666b44f43b4ba42ee82639edd0d07.webp?t=1746142050\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your hard earned credits to good use, upgrade your gear and buy new tools to make the job easier!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358680/extras/97fa02f4843c5fef192ab261fa73fe9c.webp?t=1746142050\" width=616 height=38 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 handcrafted locations 🛰️</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dangerous monsters and traps😱</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of tools and upgrades ⚙️</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satisfying prop DESTRUCTION 💥</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The joy of paying off your debt (maybe) 💸</p></li></ul>",
